OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778163069
OL,3,CShell's bumper war dividend not being
OL,4,Cused to ramp up renewable investments
OL,6,FIt's raining oil and gas money again
OL,7,Fat Shell - for now, at least.
OL,9,FThe company has reported profits of
OL,10,F$6.9 billion (#5bn) in the first three
OL,11,Fmonths of 2026, up almost 25% on the
OL,12,Fyear before.
OL,14,FLike BP, Shell is making money selling
OL,15,Ffuel to motorists.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778163069
OL,3,CShell's bumper war dividend not being
OL,4,Cused to ramp up renewable investments
OL,6,FBut the stellar profits are coming
OL,7,Ffrom elsewhere: Shell's traders have
OL,8,Fsuccessfully cashed in on volatile
OL,9,Fmovements in energy prices; its
OL,10,Frefineries are running close to full
OL,11,Fcapacity, turning oil into fuels like
OL,12,Fjet fuel and diesel, as well as
OL,13,Fchemicals for industry - products
OL,14,FShell can sell at higher prices and
OL,15,Fwith fatter margins.
OL,17,FThe company has also trimmed its costs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778163069
OL,3,CShell's bumper war dividend not being
OL,4,Cused to ramp up renewable investments
OL,6,FBut that's not the whole story. Total
OL,7,Foil and gas production fell 4%, due in
OL,8,Flarge part to the "impact of the
OL,9,FMiddle East conflict".
OL,11,FThe blockage of the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,12,Fand damage to infrastructure caused by
OL,13,Fmissile and drone attacks, is limiting
OL,14,Fwhat Shell can produce and sell.
OL,16,FA processing unit - or "train" - at
OL,17,FShell's Pearl GTL plant in Qatar, a
OL,18,Fflagship asset at Ras Laffan - one of
OL,19,Fthe most important gas hubs in the
OL,20,Fworld - was hit in March and will take
OL,21,Faround a year to repair.
OL,26,@pD@SOUqD@UO]xD@XOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778163069
OL,3,CShell's bumper war dividend not being
OL,4,Cused to ramp up renewable investments
OL,6,FThe rest of the facility is
OL,7,Funaffected, but output has been
OL,8,Freduced.
OL,10,FShell presents this as a temporary
OL,11,Fsetback, and the war as a temporary
OL,12,Fshock. It assumes energy prices will
OL,13,Feventually normalise, but does not
OL,14,Fhazard a guess as to when.
OL,16,FLast month, Shell's chief executive
OL,17,Fwas among the first industry voices to
OL,18,Fwarn that Europe could face shortages
OL,19,Fof products like diesel and jet fuel
OL,20,Fin May if the Strait of Hormuz
OL,21,Fremained closed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778163069
OL,3,CShell's bumper war dividend not being
OL,4,Cused to ramp up renewable investments
OL,6,FSpeaking to Bloomberg, Wael Sawan said
OL,7,Fthe war had led to one of the largest
OL,8,Fsupply disruptions in history - the
OL,9,Floss of the equivalent of hundreds of
OL,10,Fmillions of barrels of oil - and
OL,11,Fwarned the impact could drag on into
OL,12,Fnext year, even if a peace deal is
OL,13,Fagreed soon.
OL,15,FThe implication is clear: markets are
OL,16,Funderestimating and underpricing the
OL,17,Ffull scale of the upheaval.
OL,19,FWar in the Gulf has caused energy
OL,20,Fprices to spike and supercharged
OL,21,FShell's performance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778163069
OL,3,CShell's bumper war dividend not being
OL,4,Cused to ramp up renewable investments
OL,6,FThe company has cranked the production
OL,7,Fwheel in parts of its operations,
OL,8,Fincluding record oil volumes from
OL,9,FBrazil, but in truth it has not had to
OL,10,Fwork much harder for its windfall.
OL,12,FMoney has rolled in.
OL,14,FThe conflict in the Gulf has exposed
OL,15,Fjust how dependent we remain on
OL,16,Fhydrocarbons - and arguably
OL,17,Fstrengthened the case for accelerating
OL,18,Fthe transition away from fossil fuels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
