PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778163069
OL,3,CShell's bumper war dividend not being
OL,4,Cused to ramp up renewable investments
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FBut it's notable that Shell is not
OL,12,Fusing its windfall to ramp up
OL,13,Finvestment in renewables in any
OL,14,Fmeaningful way.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778163069
OL,3,CShell's bumper war dividend not being
OL,4,Cused to ramp up renewable investments
OL,6,FInstead, the lion's share - $5.3
OL,7,Fbillion this quarter - is being
OL,8,Freturned to shareholders, in the form
OL,9,Fof share buybacks and dividends, to
OL,10,Fthe delight of pension funds and, it
OL,11,Fshould be noted, the benefit of many
OL,12,Fpension savers.
OL,14,FInvestment is rising, but mainly in
OL,15,Foil and gas projects. Only around 10%
OL,16,Fis being channelled into lower-carbon
OL,17,Fenergy - hydrogen, carbon capture,
OL,18,Fsolar, wind and power.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778163069
OL,3,CShell's bumper war dividend not being
OL,4,Cused to ramp up renewable investments
OL,6,FThe hard truth is that, when it comes
OL,7,Fto renewables, Shell itself
OL,8,Facknowledges that "most activities
OL,9,Fwere loss-making".
OL,11,FShell has to balance the need to fund
OL,12,Fthe transition to net zero against the
OL,13,F(very real) pressure to keep
OL,14,Fshareholders happy.
OL,16,FFor now, the incentive to move faster
OL,17,Fdoesn't appear to be there - which is
OL,18,Fa problem, not least if catastrophic
OL,19,Flevels of global warming are to be
OL,20,Favoided.
OL,26,@pD@SOUqD@QO]
